# [INPUT]: Depends on root-context product and e2e image builds plus the Go workspace, Protocol, CLI, Hub, and e2e sources.
# [OUTPUT]: Restricts root Docker build contexts to sources required by Protocol-aware product and cross-product end-to-end images.
# [POS]: Serves as the repository-level Docker context boundary, excluding local binaries, App assets, docs, and VCS state.
# [PROTOCOL]: Update this header when this file changes, then review AGENTS.md
*
!go.work
!go.work.sum
!protocol/
!protocol/**
!cli/
!cli/**
!hub/
!hub/**
!e2e/
!e2e/**

cli/bin/
hub/bin/
hub/hub
hub/docs/
hub/charts/
hub/dist/
